,{"#text":5875},"  200–399",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5879,":@":5882},[5880],{"#text":5881},"1.66 (1.17–2.35)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5885,":@":5888},[5886],{"#text":5887},"1.56 (1.10–2.20)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5891,":@":5894},[5892],{"#text":5893},"1.19 (0.92–1.53)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5897,":@":5900},[5898],{"#text":5899},"1.10 (0.85–1.42)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5903,":@":5906},[5904],{"#text":5905},"1.60 (1.28–2.00)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5909,":@":5912},[5910],{"#text":5911},"1.49 (1.19–1.87)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":890},{"#text":890},{"tr":5916},[5917,5918,5923,5924,5929,5930,5935,5936,5941,5942,5947,5948,5953,5954,5959],{"#text":1464},{"td":5919,":@":5922},[5920],{"#text":5921},"  ≥400",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5925,":@":5928},[5926],{"#text":5927},"1.14 (0.60–2.18)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5931,":@":5934},[5932],{"#text":5933},"1.06 (0.56–2.03)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5937,":@":5940},[5938],{"#text":5939},"1.61 (1.05–2.49)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5943,":@":5946},[5944],{"#text":5945},"1.50 (0.97–2.31)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5949,":@":5952},[5950],{"#text":5951},"1.31 (1.06–1.61)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5955,":@":5958},[5956],{"#text":5957},"1.22 (0.99–1.51)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":890},{"#text":890},{"tr":5962},[5963,5964,5969,5970,5975,5976,5981,5982,5987,5988,5993,5994,5999,6000,6005],{"#text":1464},{"td":5965,":@":5968},[5966],{"#text":5967}," Dose–response (increment per 100 g of flecainide)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5971,":@":5974},[5972],{"#text":5973},"1.09 (0.99–1.20)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5977,":@":5980},[5978],{"#text":5979},"1.08 (0.98–1.19)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5983,":@":5986},[5984],{"#text":5985},"1.05 (0.97–1.13)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5989,":@":5992},[5990],{"#text":5991},"1.04 (0.96–1.13)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":5995,":@":5998},[5996],{"#text":5997},"0.98 (0.95–1.01)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"td":6001,":@":6004},[6002],{"#text":6003},"0.99 (0.96–1.02)",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":890},{"#text":850},{"@_valign":1687},{"#text":865},{"#text":1000},{"@_id":4877,"@_position":4866},{"#text":1000},{"p":6013},[6014],{"#text":6015},"Compared with non-users, users of flecainide (ever- and high-use) were found to have a moderate increased risk of NMSC in all databases with adjusted ORs between 1.17 and 1.39 for ever-use and 1.19 and 1.42 for high-use. However, analyses by cumulative dose in the different databases showed no consistent dose–response patterns in associations. When restricting the analyses to ever-use of flecainide, the dose–response association was also not conclusive with ORs for each incremental cumulative dose increase of 100 g of flecainide were 0.99 (0.96–1.02) in Denmark, 1.08 (0.98–1.19) in BIFAP, and 1.04 (0.96–1.13) in SIDIAP.",{"#text":1000},{"p":6018},[6019,6021,6027,6029,6035],{"#text":6020},"The association between the use of flecainide and the risk of melanoma and NMSC stratified by age and sex was carried out with ever-use as exposure for the Spanish databases (",{"xref":6022,":@":6025},[6023],{"#text":6024},"Table 3",{"@_ref-type":1433,"@_rid":6026},"T3",{"#text":6028},") and with high-use as exposure for the Danish databases (",{"xref":6030,":@":6033},[6031],{"#text":6032},"Table 4",{"@_ref-type":1433,"@_rid":6034},"T4",{"#text":6036},"). In general, the results stratified by age showed the highest estimates in the youngest age groups, but the precision was limited as reflected in the overlapping confidence intervals. When stratified by sex, all databases showed inconsistent results for both melanoma and NMSC; a higher risk of NMSC was found in male patients in the Danish databases, OR of 1.41 (1.16–1.70), and in female patients in the SIDIAP database, OR of 1.19 (1.05–1.36). In Spain, no association was observed between the ever-use of flecainide and the risk of melanoma stratified by sex, and a similar increased risk of melanoma was found in both male and female patients in Denmark.",{"#text":1000},{"table-wrap":6039,":@":6806},[6040,6041,6045,6046,6054,6055,6756,6757,6805],{"#text":865},{"label":6042},[6043],{"#text":6044},"TABLE 3",{"#text":865},{"caption":6047},[6048,6049,6053],{"#text":850},{"p":6050},[6051],{"#text":6052},"Association between ever-use of flecainide and risk of skin cancer, according to patient subgroups in the Spanish databases (SIDIAP and BIFAP). Reference: Never-users of flecainide in each subgroup (unexposed).",{"#text":865},{"#text":865},{"table":6056},[6057,6058,6138,6139,6755],{"#text":850},{"thead":6059,":@":6137},[6060,6061,6080,6081,6136],{"#text":890},{"tr":6062},[6063,6064,6067,6068,6073,6074,6079],{"#text":1464},{"th":6065,":@":6066},[],{"@_align":1468},{"#text":1464},{"th":6069,":@":6072},[6070],{"#text":6071},"BIFAP database",{"@_colspan":795,"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"th":6075,":@":6078},[6076],{"#text":6077},"SIDIAP database",{"@_colspan":795,"@_align":1475},{"#text":890},{"#text":890},{"tr":6082},[6083,6084,6088,6089,6094,6095,6100,6101,6112,6113,6117,6118,6122,6123,6135],{"#text":1464},{"th":6085,":@":6087},[6086],{"#text":1527},{"@_align":1468},{"#text":1464},{"th":6090,":@":6093},[6091],{"#text":6092},"Cases exposed/unexposed",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"th":6096,":@":6099},[6097],{"#text":6098},"Controls exposed/unexposed",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"th":6102,":@":6111},[6103,6104],{"#text":4937},{"xref":6105,":@":6109},[6106],{"sup":6107},[6108],{"#text":4941},{"@_ref-type":1504,"@_rid":6110},"Tfn3",{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"th":6114,":@":6116},[6115],{"#text":6092},{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"th":6119,":@":6121},[6120],{"#text":6098},{"@_align":1475},{"#text":1464},{"th":6124,":@":6134},[6125,6127],{"#text":6126},"Or (95% CI)",{"xref":6128,":@":6132},[6129],{"sup":6130},[6131],{"#text":4950},{"@_